Storyline

When Anastasia Steele, a literature student, goes to interview the wealthy 
Christian Grey as a favor to her roommate Kate Kavanagh, she encounters 
a beautiful, brilliant and intimidating man. The innocent and naive Ana 
starts to realize she wants him. Despite his enigmatic reserve and advice, 
she finds herself desperate to get close to him. Not able to resist Ana's beauty 
and independent spirit, Christian Grey admits he wants her too, but on his 
own terms. Ana hesitates as she discovers the singular tastes of Christian 
Grey - despite the embellishments of success, his multinational businesses, 
his vast wealth, and his loving family, Grey is consumed by the need to 
control everything.
